Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.43,0:00:20.56,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.76,0:00:22.93,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.14,0:00:29.73,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.99,0:00:40.45,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.58,0:00:43.87,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.12,0:00:49.25,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between the sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.63,0:00:55.63,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.84,0:01:02.60,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good time just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.89,0:01:07.06,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.14,0:01:09.31,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.44,0:01:16.07,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.49,0:01:26.66,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.83,0:01:30.17,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.33,0:01:35.63,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.92,0:01:41.89,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing, let's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.10,0:01:48.94,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave the rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.02,0:01:53.19,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.32,0:01:55.53,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.61,0:01:59.91,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.03,0:02:02.45,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.99,0:02:04.66,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.74,0:02:06.20,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.37,0:02:07.91,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.04,0:02:09.54,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.67,0:02:11.17,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.25,0:02:13.04,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.13,0:02:14.38,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.42,0:02:15.55,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.59,0:02:19.68,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.80,0:02:22.01,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.09,0:02:26.39,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.47,0:02:28.73,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.77,0:02:32.77,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.98,0:02:35.19,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.32,0:02:39.57,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.70,0:02:42.28,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.95,0:02:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.24,0:02:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.00,0:02:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.08,0:02:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.42,0:03:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.38,0:03:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.75,0:03:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.59,0:03:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.24,0:03:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I left everything this world \Nhas to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.47,0:03:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto theGrand Line
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.91,0:03:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.56,0:03:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.86,0:03:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, come on board, Franky...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.74,0:03:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Board my ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.57,0:03:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so cocky!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.78,0:03:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I don't have much choice \Nbut to help you guys out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.58,0:03:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Franky, will be the shipwright on your ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.42,0:03:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Rejoice!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.37,0:03:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.55,0:03:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although we said all sorts of things\Nto each other, we're friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.01,0:03:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let these little things go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.01,0:03:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.40,0:03:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.35,0:03:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's what you want...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.02,0:03:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...let me say one last thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.57,0:03:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.65,0:04:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.69,0:04:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for being bullheaded!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.45,0:04:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.62,0:04:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.96,0:04:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.13,0:04:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.97,0:04:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grab my hand already!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.76,0:04:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think about this\Nfor the ship's name, Franky?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.77,0:04:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pirate ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.18,0:04:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Thousand Sunny!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.15,0:04:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coup de Burst!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.99,0:04:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It consumes three barrels of cola,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.98,0:04:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it lets us fly one kilometer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.53,0:04:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing the Going Merry\Ncould do that this ship can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.25,0:05:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It exceeds the Merry in every way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.21,0:05:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Merry's brave soul will be
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.08,0:05:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,inherited by the Thousand Sunny.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.63,0:05:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.22,0:05:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, once again...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.68,0:05:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To Robin and Usopp, who came back to us,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.84,0:05:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to our new friend, Franky...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.10,0:05:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and to our pirate ship, the Thousand Sunny!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.98,0:05:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.89,0:05:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.10,0:05:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.19,0:05:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our next destination is Fishman Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.23,0:05:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.34,0:05:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't, Vigaro...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.65,0:06:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa, are you looking at your\Ncollection by yourself again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.36,0:06:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.42,0:06:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is everyone already here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.03,0:06:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were awfully quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.86,0:06:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to get started\Non the preparations now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.12,0:06:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make sure that you have\Na special birthday, Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.05,0:06:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Swap out with me, Jiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.52,0:06:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go get some sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.84,0:06:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep an eye on the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.05,0:06:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Mysterious Band of Pirates!\NSunny and the Dangerous Trap"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.11,0:06:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, this is bliss!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.88,0:06:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pure bliss!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.74,0:07:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing beats bathing in a massive\Ntub that sways on the waves!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.75,0:07:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whee!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This here is my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.34,0:07:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"What seems to be the problem?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.70,0:07:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.21,0:07:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.52,0:07:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I'll\Nget a patient anytime soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.22,0:07:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught something!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.40,0:07:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I got a cool shark!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.68,0:07:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put it in! Put it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.06,0:07:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's put it in the aquarium!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.14,0:07:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.23,0:07:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In ya go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.10,0:07:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.98,0:07:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They dropped in another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.39,0:07:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it a shark?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.44,0:07:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.06,0:07:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this a nice room?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.91,0:07:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The room's great,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.22,0:07:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I can't believe those \Nidiots tossed in a shark!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.37,0:07:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.14,0:07:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now let's go see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.04,0:07:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's check out the aquarium!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.58,0:07:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.79,0:07:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did a shark come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.41,0:07:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an awesome one with horns!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.96,0:07:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it did, but you've lost all\Nof the other fish you caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.01,0:07:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think about compatibility\N before you throw something in!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.87,0:07:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that a no-brainer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.55,0:08:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.73,0:08:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This punk's gonna be tonight's dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.89,0:08:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji, roast it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.48,0:08:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll barbecue that stupid shark!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.89,0:08:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you amateur!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.70,0:08:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still a fresh fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.90,0:08:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should either make sushi or serve it\Nboiled with a hot and sour miso sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.53,0:08:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tempura might be nice, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.82,0:08:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starting to get hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.70,0:08:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But seriously, thank you\Nfor this great ship, Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.75,0:08:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no biggie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.41,0:08:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you still haven't seen\N its true power yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.46,0:08:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its true power?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.79,0:08:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.61,0:08:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This ship's key features are\N its "Soldier Dock System."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.80,0:08:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are five docks ranging from\NChannel 0 to Channel 4 located on the bilge.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.47,0:08:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Each dock is rigged to\Nhandle different situations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.89,0:08:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of them will play a unique role\Nin assisting the Thousand Sunny!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.26,0:08:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.27,0:08:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then lemme see them in action!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.65,0:08:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hold your horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.32,0:08:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you see them as they're needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.90,0:09:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be a shame to show them off all at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.74,0:09:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hardly wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.64,0:09:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boo! Boo! Boo! Boo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.12,0:09:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a great bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.33,0:09:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it seemed a lot colder\Nthan yesterday, and I was right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.42,0:09:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we've entered\Na winter island's currents.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.30,0:09:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Kokoro-san never mentioned\Nanything about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.98,0:09:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's snowing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.27,0:09:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay, it's snowing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.56,0:09:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.56,0:09:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.61,0:09:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.90,0:09:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're spoiling the party!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.53,0:09:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is how you're supposed\Nto act when it snows:
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.61,0:09:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Guys, it's snowing!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.05,0:09:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you still didn't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.50,0:09:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.06,0:09:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really aren't that bright!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.20,0:09:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dumb-dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.95,0:09:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing ticks me off more than\Nhaving them call me names!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.34,0:09:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.39,0:09:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen snow in ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.13,0:09:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it'll stick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.35,0:10:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope it does!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.05,0:10:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should make something\Nwarm for dinner tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.24,0:10:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there's a ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.12,0:10:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something seems a bit off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.87,0:10:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems off?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.83,0:10:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.25,0:10:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What gives?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.53,0:10:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't have any sails,\N let alone an ensign.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.21,0:10:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't have any sails?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.49,0:10:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means it's just floating there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.71,0:10:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's either a ship in distress, or it's a...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.26,0:10:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.45,0:10:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,some pirates play a nasty game \Ncalled the "Davy Back Fight."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.26,0:10:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.22,0:10:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't think...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.18,0:10:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they fell victim to that game, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.02,0:10:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.84,0:10:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some people just came out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.32,0:11:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fishing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.90,0:11:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They must be in distress.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.78,0:11:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They look horribly exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.20,0:11:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.24,0:11:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, let's go check on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.45,0:11:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they end up being our enemy,\Nwe'll just send them flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.72,0:11:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't any fish out there that'll\Nbite a hook without bait, are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.39,0:11:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.48,0:11:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't even say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.87,0:11:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It beats doing nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.64,0:11:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got time to kill,\Nso let's be patient and wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.36,0:11:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.40,0:11:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you guys all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.66,0:11:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.87,0:11:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.28,0:11:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.89,0:11:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Make a break for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.96,0:11:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rudder doesn't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.67,0:11:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we don't have any sails!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.54,0:12:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please show mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.80,0:12:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.43,0:12:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dang, both you and your ship are\Nin sorry shape! You're both a mess!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.44,0:12:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.23,0:12:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-We're just humble fishermen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.65,0:12:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fishermen?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.90,0:12:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.67,0:12:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About three days ago, we were\Nattacked by an unidentified ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.91,0:12:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only did they steal all\Nof our valuables and food,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.04,0:12:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they also trashed our sail\Nand destroyed our rudder.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.33,0:12:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been floating out here ever since!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.87,0:12:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you've got nothing to gain by attacking us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.79,0:12:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No worries there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.56,0:12:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long story short, all of \Nyou are hungry, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.01,0:12:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were just about to eat, so come join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.26,0:12:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.06,0:12:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.14,0:12:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.05,0:12:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.12,0:12:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My cook can't turn a blind \Neye to guys like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.14,0:12:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be strangers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.43,0:13:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.17,0:13:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it ready yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.38,0:13:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're starving!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.40,0:13:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's just about ready,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.88,0:13:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but first...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.40,0:13:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.55,0:13:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been dying to get some patients.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.02,0:13:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go tend to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.12,0:13:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.58,0:13:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For starters, let's have\Nanyone injured come see me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.33,0:13:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.12,0:13:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is anyone too badly hurt to move?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.08,0:13:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their pet just talked!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.25,0:13:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a pet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.88,0:13:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a pirate, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.09,0:13:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worth a whopping 50 Berries! Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.79,0:13:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.53,0:13:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sit still.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.90,0:13:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose these are rookie\Npirates who just hit the seas
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.61,0:13:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with their new ship and stars still in their eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.29,0:13:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Click.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.12,0:14:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.29,0:14:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.47,0:14:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do things look over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.42,0:14:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.88,0:14:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, we're in the middle\Nof winning a pirate crew over...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.06,0:14:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,uh, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.80,0:14:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.72,0:14:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what does their\NJolly Roger look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.68,0:14:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, it's a skull wearing a straw hat, I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.39,0:14:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.51,0:14:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like you'd go hunting\Nfor bugs out on the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.68,0:14:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What could they be thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.09,0:14:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make small talk with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.65,0:14:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.73,0:14:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Now listen to me carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.92,0:14:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are the Straw Hats,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.07,0:14:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with a total bounty of\N600 million Berries on their heads!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.41,0:14:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,600 million, sir?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.37,0:14:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.00,0:14:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what you must do, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.46,0:14:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, all too well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.50,0:14:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, don't you dare let\Nthem escape before we arrive!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.51,0:14:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Click.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.34,0:14:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,600 million Berries on their heads...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.40,0:15:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.50,0:15:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is too good, Mister Eyebrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.62,0:15:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.81,0:15:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so good it's making me cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.37,0:15:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they crying drunks?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.75,0:15:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.77,0:15:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You ladies sure are cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.96,0:15:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure are!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.57,0:15:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so cute you're making me cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.42,0:15:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it would seem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.84,0:15:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they were late to notice us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.35,0:15:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.81,0:15:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.90,0:15:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.86,0:15:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you leave to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.36,0:15:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.03,0:15:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.07,0:15:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor, after seeing what you can do,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.76,0:16:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there is someone else I'd like you to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.70,0:16:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you follow me aboard our ship right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.41,0:16:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.93,0:16:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.73,0:16:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're headed straight \Nfor the New World?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.18,0:16:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one will think any less of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.50,0:16:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn around now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.06,0:16:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hell over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.48,0:16:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.12,0:16:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.48,0:16:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.90,0:16:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, we've only heard rumors...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.95,0:16:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Supposedly it's a horrible place!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.57,0:16:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.73,0:16:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care what the rumors claim.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.29,0:16:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll find out for myself if it's\Nlike hell when I get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.50,0:16:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.38,0:16:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.55,0:17:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like you've been\Nlooking after my men for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.64,0:17:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let show you my gratitude!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.50,0:17:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm their commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.05,0:17:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The name's Stansen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.02,0:17:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my best brew,\Nwhich I had specially ordered!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.48,0:17:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please help yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.81,0:17:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.66,0:17:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really have a patient down here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.66,0:17:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.93,0:17:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where does\Nhe think he's taking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.83,0:18:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is that the patient?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.71,0:18:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.59,0:18:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His entire body is seriously injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.25,0:18:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been days since the\Nlast time he was conscious...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.55,0:18:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.83,0:18:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to help him get better!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.63,0:18:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.54,0:18:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.76,0:18:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His wounds are festering!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.18,0:18:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you let him get this bad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.27,0:18:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I had a choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.39,0:18:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not safe to move him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.07,0:18:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to begin the\N operation right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.28,0:18:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This has a unique flavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.57,0:18:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you had booze, even though\Nyou didn't have anything to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.37,0:18:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty much!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.42,0:18:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, wow, this is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.66,0:18:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like finding a port in a storm!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.91,0:18:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We really ought to do more to thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.17,0:18:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't sweat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.63,0:19:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't an option!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.03,0:19:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really must drop by our port
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.97,0:19:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we can thank you properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.68,0:19:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Drop by our port"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.54,0:19:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, you want us\N to take you there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.89,0:19:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You caught on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.84,0:19:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good guess!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.14,0:19:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're one funny man!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.86,0:19:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, we'll take ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.19,0:19:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.26,0:19:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.85,0:19:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.52,0:19:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Fishman Island?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.98,0:19:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we visit any of the other islands,\Nit'll change our log's course.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.53,0:19:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't it be fine if we leave\Nas soon as we drop them off?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.03,0:19:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon! What's the big deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.93,0:19:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're in need of help!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.16,0:19:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I'm glad you have such\Nan understanding captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.58,0:19:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm counting on you to get us there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.73,0:19:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, they say that the people\Nyou travel with make the journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.11,0:20:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'd say we're due for another "cheers"!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.15,0:20:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sounds good!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.15,0:20:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.36,0:20:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a hilarious captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.58,0:20:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is he, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.91,0:20:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've done everything I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.36,0:20:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now all we can do now is wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.00,0:20:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.84,0:20:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let our guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.92,0:20:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He isn't over the worst of it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.12,0:20:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.08,0:20:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.52,0:20:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.04,0:20:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not excited about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.62,0:21:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were such considerate guys, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.32,0:21:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,True enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.73,0:21:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the girls were cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.71,0:21:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you say that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.10,0:21:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have a choice in the matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.05,0:21:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.10,0:21:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we lay claim to this amazing ship, I bet we could take them on!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.01,0:21:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.35,0:21:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are going to hand this ship over to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.18,0:21:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are merely going to carry out\Nwhatever missions they assign to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.10,0:21:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you call this a "mission"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.86,0:21:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Count us out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.48,0:21:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to steal this ship\N and prepare to strike back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.82,0:21:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As things stand now, Vigaro will\Nnever be able to rest in peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.03,0:21:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, punks!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.07,0:21:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're free to argue \Namongst yourselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.70,0:21:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I don't like the direction\Nthis conversation's going.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.45,0:21:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Weren't you sound asleep?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.21,0:21:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The smell of anesthesia was so\Nstrong that I couldn't fall asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.21,0:21:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You ruined my cuisine with that nasty drug!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.51,0:21:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You better be prepared to\Npay for what you've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.35,0:21:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The three of them can\Nhandle this on their own...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.74,0:22:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.17,0:22:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Click.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.58,0:22:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.75,0:22:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have managed to successfully\Ndrive the prey into a tight corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.79,0:22:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.84,0:22:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some rookies are currently\Nonboard their ship right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.09,0:22:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Them?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.46,0:22:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've proven surprisingly useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.70,0:22:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, if I may be so bold,\Nit's still too soon to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.21,0:22:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, they have hooked a rather large fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.64,0:22:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A large fish?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.85,0:22:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.74,0:22:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy and his \NStraw Hat Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.77,0:22:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their total bounty comes to 660 million Berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.61,0:22:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.21,0:22:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How appropriate\Nfor such a splendid day.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.24,0:22:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.77,0:22:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It certainly is!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.41,0:23:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.70,0:23:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir! You can leave this to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.08,0:23:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But honestly, you know, this really--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.83,0:23:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Click.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.09,0:23:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I expect this to turn into quite the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.44,0:23:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it troublesome when\Nyou have unexpected guests?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.77,0:23:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can deal with guests!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.73,0:23:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, aren't we completely\Nsurrounded by Navy ships?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.03,0:23:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem somewhat happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.65,0:23:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you this ship's super powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.82,0:23:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.33,0:23:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Sunny's in a Pinch!\NRoar, Secret Super-Speed Mecha"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.83,0:23:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
